<subSubSection id="0B7639DACB8601C5B2F30DBEF6617FC9" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" type="description">
<paragraph id="CBE980C6381F91C82296BF94D05FD548" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0B06D565F2568946C155B3B5A35C4D08" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">
Animal of medium to large size, up to 45 mm long in examined specimens. Oval to elongate oval, slightly depressed, color of tegmentum greenish-brown to dark brown. Head valve semicircular, front slope straight, posterior margin V-shaped. Intermediate valves broadly rectangular. Tail valve less than semicircular, almost as wide as head valve. Girdle profusely beset with very long (up to 10 mm) thick, coarse, corneous hairs, not only interspersed throughout girdle but in girdle bridges, protruding at sutures and extending over valves. Tegmentum pustulose sculptured with minute and neatly separated pustules, on the end valves the pustules are arranged in radiating rows. Body width/length, mean 0.66; height/length, mean 0.22 (After 
<bibRefCitation id="3F8863427EC09844963068B0D4A8207D" author="Ferreira, JA" journalOrPublisher="Veliger" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" pagination="203 - 224" title="The genus Chaetopleura Shuttleworth, 1853 in the warm temperate and tropical Eastern Pacific, Southern California to Peru, with the description of two new species." volume="25" year="1983">Ferreira 1983</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="9028B447C90A40AF4D3F2981EF09419F" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" type="material examined">
<paragraph id="8A8BE8645C42126E82B607E256C89A48" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AB9C5DC08FE54D4619DE45AB54EA17E2" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">Specimens found in almost all locations, with the exception of Bahia Cisne, Puerto Viejo and Playa Rodillo up to Obispito (Table 1). Calderilla (MPCCL 3072014C, 1 specimen).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FE68168D3E8D059385001A48AEA9406A" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="565C6960DB6628D4234C01433E164DC7" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">Distribution.</paragraph>
