<bibRefCitation id="5347B1C3A69105FB4B7A87D952C2FA7B" author="Kaas, P" journalOrPublisher="EJ Brill and W Backhuys, Leiden" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" title="Monograph of Living Chitons (Mollusca: Polyplacophora) (Volume 3) - Suborder Ischnochitonina. lschnochitonidae: Chaetopleurinae, &amp; Ischnochitoninae (pars). Additions to Vols 1 &amp; 2" year="1987">Kaas and Van Belle (1987)</bibRefCitation>
cited this species along the western coast of South America, between Cape San Lorenzo (
<geoCoordinate id="F45A8627A835D03D44E298B0EEDF5F72" direction="south" orientation="latitude" precision="15" value="-1.0666667">
1°4
<normalizedToken id="2DFF3ECB07EE8C1FB5D760A479297FFF" originalValue="’0”">'0&quot;</normalizedToken>
S
</geoCoordinate>
; 
<geoCoordinate id="77A555133D355847C02D9A73734E8FB4" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="15" value="-80.933334">
80°55
<normalizedToken id="1D2EBDB9C86780CBED82E50580F9251A" originalValue="’60”">'60&quot;</normalizedToken>
W
</geoCoordinate>
), Ecuador to the Chonos Archipelago (
<geoCoordinate id="E7568A9234B924DB5506A323E6E930A2" direction="south" orientation="latitude" precision="15" value="-45.0">
45°0
<normalizedToken id="0649FCF6EB8BD6FE78089C56B12FC1EC" originalValue="’0”">'0&quot;</normalizedToken>
S
</geoCoordinate>
; 
<geoCoordinate id="B53BD29CDA6C868AC1133A41C8225A0F" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="15" value="-74.0">
74°0
<normalizedToken id="A422D71B887A303BF603DCCDA2169793" originalValue="’0”">'0&quot;</normalizedToken>
W
</geoCoordinate>
), southern Chile. This species lives in the intertidal zone down to a depth of 40 m (
<bibRefCitation id="755B7722E32A70D0ACB3F803642A9D0A" author="Kaas, P" journalOrPublisher="EJ Brill and W Backhuys, Leiden" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" title="Monograph of Living Chitons (Mollusca: Polyplacophora) (Volume 3) - Suborder Ischnochitonina. lschnochitonidae: Chaetopleurinae, &amp; Ischnochitoninae (pars). Additions to Vols 1 &amp; 2" year="1987">Kaas and Van Belle 1987</bibRefCitation>
